    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 栈帧结构示意</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">methodA</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">x</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">10</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">              </span><span class="c1">// 局部变量表</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">methodB</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">               </span><span class="c1">// 操作数栈压入返回地址</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">methodB</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">Object</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">obj</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Object</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="c1">// obj引用在栈，对象在堆</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="gc垃圾回收分代收集基于弱分代假设">GC垃圾回收：分代收集基于&quot;弱分代假设&quot;</h3>
<p><strong>弱分代假设</strong>：大部分对象朝生夕死，熬过越多次GC的对象越可能长期存活。</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>